{"tid":887460,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過同網友見面，發現同想像中差好遠","createTime":"2018-11-03T02:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T05:45:39.000Z","uid":68734,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7f36aec3cb0b4fb323e74e593161d929074c039c","tid":887460,"uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"最近上網配對識左個女仔<br />\n差不多日日傾左兩個月，一直都覺得佢係好乖、好靜個種女仔<br />\n但我一直都無問佢拎電話、facebook<br />\n<br />\n前幾日忍唔住約左佢出來，了解左後先知佢同想像中差好遠... <br />\n無估到佢係會約男仔影私影個種，再睇返facebook上面個d相... 真係接受唔到<br />\n<br />\n我都諗住斷，但傾左咁耐難免有種不捨<br />\n但捨不得既<br />\n其實係一個唔存在既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fab2ede0d94cb5a2e8a8ea513bff740cc981ae","tid":887460,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:46:21.000Z","msg":"私影雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dc2489a6c5ee1fb9e4d31784e5c6262459d263","tid":887460,"uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5fab2ede0d94cb5a2e8a8ea513bff740cc981ae","tid":887460,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:46:21.000Z","msg":"私影雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:47:38.000Z","msg":"唉... 真係接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要有拍過上酒店影個種"},{"pid":"137fa55c48d1257fd2908f5d763fef082e1b6dde","tid":887460,"uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"點解想簡簡單單識個女仔都咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我寧願佢係樣子中下個種"},{"pid":"2b0e0343fb38a38644febd32ebb823ed8ab5755b","tid":887460,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18dc2489a6c5ee1fb9e4d31784e5c6262459d263","tid":887460,"uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5fab2ede0d94cb5a2e8a8ea513bff740cc981ae","tid":887460,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0